#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_parallax
msgid ""
"<i>“One of the great beauties of architecture is that each time, it is like "
"life starting all over again.”</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>“ໜຶ່ງໃນຄວາມງາມທີ່ຍິ່ງໃຫຍ່ຂອງສະຖາປັດຕະຍະກຳ ຄືການທີ່ແຕ່ລະຄັ້ງ ມັນປຽບເໝືອນຊີວິດທີ່ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນໃໝ່ອີກຄັ້ງ.”</"
"i>"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_banner
msgid "A Different Viewpoint."
msgstr "ມຸມມອງທີ່ແຕກຕ່າງ."

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_call_to_action
msgid "As <b>436 clients</b> before you, let’s work together"
msgstr "ຄືກັບ <b>ລູກຄ້າ 436 ລາຍ</b> ກ່ອນໜ້າທ່ານ, ມາຮ່ວມມືກັນເທາະ"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_text_image
msgid "Building Castle in Cloud"
msgstr "ການສ້າງຜົນງານໃນລະບົບ Cloud"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_media_list
msgid "Construction site"
msgstr "ສະຖານທີ່ກໍ່ສ້າງ"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_picture
msgid "Creating places that enhance the human experience."
msgstr "ການສ້າງສະຖານທີ່ທີ່ຍົກລະດັບປະສົບການຂອງມະນຸດ."

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_banner
msgid "Discover More"
msgstr "ຄົ້ນຫາເພີ່ມເຕີມ"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.enark_snippet_options
msgid "Gradients"
msgstr "ສີໄລ່ລະດັບ"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_media_list
msgid "Know our clients."
msgstr "ຮູ້ຈັກກັບລູກຄ້າຂອງພວກເຮົາ."

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_media_list
msgid "Nature friendly"
msgstr "ເປັນມິດກັບທຳມະຊາດ"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.enark_snippet_options
msgid "None"
msgstr "ບໍ່ມີ"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_media_list
msgid ""
"Our creations integrate and are in perfect harmony with their environment."
msgstr ""
"ຜົນງານສ້າງສັນຂອງພວກເຮົາປະສົມປະສານ ແລະ ມີຄວາມກົມກືນຢ່າງສົມບູນກັບສະພາບແວດລ້ອມ."

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_media_list
msgid ""
"Our mastery of construction techniques has been built up over time through "
"our close collaboration with the workers and our sustained presence on the "
"construction sites."
msgstr ""
"ຄວາມຊຳນານໃນເຕັກນິກການກໍ່ສ້າງຂອງພວກເຮົາໄດ້ຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນຕາມການເວລາ ຜ່ານການຮ່ວມມືຢ່າງໃກ້ຊິດກັບຄົນງານ "
"ແລະ ການມີສ່ວນຮ່ວມຢ່າງຕໍ່ເນື່ອງໃນສະຖານທີ່ກໍ່ສ້າງ."

#. module: theme_enark
#: model:ir.model,name:theme_enark.model_theme_utils
msgid "Theme Utils"
msgstr "ເຄື່ອງມືຊ່ວຍຈັດການທີມ (Theme Utils)"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_picture
msgid "We always put people and nature at the center of our projects."
msgstr "ພວກເຮົາຖືເອົາຄົນ ແລະ ທຳມະຊາດເປັນສູນກາງຂອງໂຄງການຂອງພວກເຮົາສະເໝີ."

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_media_list
msgid ""
"We always start by exploring our clients goals, priorities, lifestyle, and "
"tastes."
msgstr ""
"ພວກເຮົາເລີ່ມຕົ້ນສະເໝີດ້ວຍການສຳຫຼວດເປົ້າໝາຍ, ບຸລິມະສິດ, ວິຖີຊີວິດ, ແລະ ລົດນິຍົມຂອງລູກຄ້າ."

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_banner
msgid ""
"We are a contemporary architecture firm working mainly in the residential, "
"commercial and office sectors. Our projects are built all over the world, in"
" urban and rural environments."
msgstr ""
"ພວກເຮົາແມ່ນບໍລິສັດສະຖາປັດຕະຍະກຳຮ່ວມສະໄໝທີ່ເຮັດວຽກຫຼັກໆໃນຂະແໜງທີ່ຢູ່ອາໄສ, ການຄ້າ ແລະ ຫ້ອງການ. ໂຄ"
"ງການຂອງພວກເຮົາຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນທົ່ວໂລກ, ທັງໃນສະພາບແວດລ້ອມຕົວເມືອງ ແລະ ຊົນນະບົດ."

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_text_image
msgid ""
"When designing an architectural concept, we take into account the nine "
"criteria that Zumthor considers to be important in creating an architectural"
" atmosphere."
msgstr ""
"ໃນເວລາອອກແບບແນວຄວາມຄິດທາງສະຖາປັດຕະຍະກຳ, ພວກເຮົາຄຳນຶງເຖິງເກົ້າເກນທີ່ Zumthor ຖືວ່າສຳຄັນໃນກ"
"ານສ້າງບັນຍາກາດທາງສະຖາປັດຕະຍະກຳ."
